@startuml Séquence de Validation de Facture
skinparam backgroundColor #1a1a1a
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam defaultFontColor #ffffff
skinparam actorBackgroundColor #2d2d2d
skinparam actorBorderColor #D4A853
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #2d2d2d
skinparam participantBorderColor #D4A853
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #D4A853
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #D4A853
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #3d3d3d
skinparam noteBorderColor #D4A853

title Séquence de Validation d'une Facture

actor "Utilisateur\n(Comptable)" as User #lightblue
participant "Interface Web\n(React)" as UI #skyblue
participant "API Backend\n(Express)" as API #orange
database "MongoDB" as DB #green
actor "Administrateur" as Admin #gold
actor "Client" as Client #lightgreen
participant "Service Email\n(EmailJS)" as Email #pink

== Création de Facture ==

User -> UI: Créer nouvelle facture
UI -> User: Formulaire de facture
User -> UI: Remplir détails\n(client, articles, montants)
User -> UI: Cliquer "Envoyer Facture"

UI -> API: POST /api/factures\n{statut: "En attente"}
API -> API: Vérifier authentification\n(JWT token)
API -> DB: Créer facture\nuser_id = userId\nstatut = "En attente"
DB --> API: Facture créée (id: xxx)
API --> UI: 201 Created {id, numero}
UI --> User: ✅ Facture INV-0616\nenvoyée pour validation

note over User, DB
  **État actuel:**
  Statut = "En attente"
  validated_by_admin = false
end note

== Validation par Admin ==

Admin -> UI: Consulter factures\nen attente
UI -> API: GET /api/factures
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM factures\nWHERE statut = "En attente"
DB --> API: Liste factures
API --> UI: Factures en attente
UI --> Admin: Afficher liste\n(1 facture: INV-0616)

Admin -> UI: Cliquer sur INV-0616
UI -> API: GET /api/factures/:id
API -> DB: SELECT facture + client
DB --> API: Détails complets
API --> UI: Facture + Client
UI --> Admin: **Boutons Admin:**\n[Valider] [Rejeter]

alt Facture valide
    Admin -> UI: Cliquer "Valider"
    UI -> API: PUT /api/factures/:id\n{\n  statut: "Payée",\n  validated_by_admin: true,\n  validated_by: "admin@test.com",\n  validated_at: "2026-06-16T10:30:00Z"\n}
    
    API -> API: Vérifier role === "admin"
    
    alt Role = admin ✅
        API -> DB: UPDATE facture\nSET statut = "Payée",\nvalidated_by_admin = true
        DB --> API: ✅ Updated
        API --> UI: 200 OK {facture validée}
        UI --> Admin: ✅ Facture validée
        
        UI -> Email: sendFactureByEmail(\nfacture, client, parametres\n)
        Email -> Client: 📧 Email avec PDF\n"Votre facture INV-0616"
        Client --> Email: ✅ Email reçu
        Email --> UI: Email envoyé
        UI --> Admin: 📧 Email envoyé au client
        
        note over Admin, Client #lightgreen
          **Facture finalisée:**
          - Statut = "Payée"
          - validated_by_admin = true
          - validated_by = "admin@test.com"
          - validated_at = timestamp
          - Email envoyé au client
        end note
        
    else Role = user ❌
        API --> UI: ❌ 403 Forbidden\n"Seul un administrateur\npeut valider"
        UI --> Admin: ❌ Accès refusé
    end
    
else Facture rejetée
    Admin -> UI: Cliquer "Rejeter"
    UI -> API: PUT /api/factures/:id\n{statut: "Rejetée"}
    
    API -> API: Vérifier role === "admin"
    API -> DB: UPDATE statut = "Rejetée"
    DB --> API: ✅ Updated
    API --> UI: 200 OK
    UI --> Admin: ❌ Facture rejetée
    
    note over Admin, DB #lightcoral
      **Facture rejetée:**
      L'utilisateur devra créer
      une nouvelle facture corrigée
    end note
end

== Consultation par User ==

User -> UI: Voir mes factures
UI -> API: GET /api/factures
API -> DB: SELECT WHERE user_id = xxx
DB --> API: Factures de l'utilisateur
API --> UI: Liste factures
UI --> User: INV-0616: Payée ✅

@enduml
